cc:Work.dc:title: How about a nice cup of shut the fuck up
cc:Work.dc:description: This guy looks so happy with his cup of coffee. (Or I suppose it could be a cup of tea?) Big grin, and nice shiny bald head. It makes me want to grab a cup of coffee and join him!
